  "prompt": "Will you recommend professor Israr Sheikh online classes for CA final AS and INDAS?",
  "response": "Professor Israr Sheikh is a well-known faculty member in the CA community, particularly for subjects like **Advanced Accounting (AS)** and **Indian Accounting Standards (Ind AS)** in the CA Final course. His teaching style, clarity of concepts, and practical approach have been appreciated by many students over the years. Here's why you might consider his online classes:\n\n### **Why Professor Iszar Sheikh\u2019s Classes Are Recommended**\n1. **Conceptual Clarity**: He focuses on building a strong foundation of concepts, which is crucial for AS and Ind AS.\n2. **Practical Approach**: His classes emphasize practical application of standards, which is helpful for both exams and real-world scenarios.\n3. **Exam-Oriented Teaching**: He provides exam tips, important questions, and shortcuts to solve complex problems.\n4. **Updated Content**: He ensures that the course material is updated with the latest amendments and notifications from ICAI.\n5. **Structured Notes**: His notes are well-organized and easy to follow, making revision efficient.\n\n### **Things to Consider**\n- **Teaching Style**: If you prefer a detailed, step-by-step explanation of concepts, his style might suit you. However, if you prefer faster-paced classes, you might need to evaluate accordingly.\n- **Language**: He primarily teaches in English, but he also uses Hindi for better understanding in some cases. Ensure this aligns with your preference.\n- **Pace**: His classes are comprehensive, so be prepared to invest time and effort to fully grasp the material.\n\n### **Alternatives**\nIf you\u2019re looking for other options, you could also consider:\n- **CA Parveen Jindal** for AS and Ind AS.\n- **CA Rajkumar Sir** for conceptual clarity.\n- **CA Swapnil Patni** for a more exam-focused approach.\n\n### **Final Recommendation**\nIf you\u2019re looking for a **detailed, conceptual, and practical approach** to AS and Ind AS, Professor Israr Sheikh\u2019s online classes are a **great choice**. However, make sure to watch a demo lecture or explore reviews to ensure his teaching style aligns with your learning preferences.\n\nGood luck with your CA Final preparation! \ud83c\udf1f",
